Class CastExpr

java.lang.Object
  ast.ASTNode
      ast.Expr
          ast.CastExpr

public class CastExpr
extends Expr

The CastExpr class represents a cast expression. It contains a target type name (type), an expression to cast (expr), and a flag indicating whether the cast is an upcast (upcast).

See Also:
ASTNode, Expr
